    "name": "Doctor Life Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 3075060,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075060/extras/57d19a5f10d94fb52f8232fe22cb114f.poster.avif?t=1766945750\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075060/extras/57d19a5f10d94fb52f8232fe22cb114f.webm?t=1766945750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075060/extras/57d19a5f10d94fb52f8232fe22cb114f.mp4?t=1766945750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>诊断你的病人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位病人都有自己的故事，而他们的症状正是揭开谜底的关键。从普通感冒到危及生命的疾病，你的任务是找出真正的问题所在。利用各种诊断工具，如血液检测、体温测量和心率监测器，拼凑出完整的病情图景。每个病例都带来独特的挑战，让你时刻保持警惕，做出最佳决策。<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是否具备揭开真相的技能和直觉？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075060/extras/c374210c1f16b21ab24a39f3cb90958b.poster.avif?t=1766945750\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075060/extras/c374210c1f16b21ab24a39f3cb90958b.webm?t=1766945750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075060/extras/c374210c1f16b21ab24a39f3cb90958b.mp4?t=1766945750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>管理你的医院</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的诊所起初规模较小，但通过努力，你可以将其发展成繁忙的医疗中心。投资升级<strong>病房</strong>，让患者在你的照料下康复，或扩建<strong>核磁共振室</strong>，解锁先进的诊断能力。升级设备，雇佣更多员工，以应对日益增长的需求。<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成功运营一家医院不仅仅是资源管理，更需要在效率与同理心之间取得平衡。保持病人满意，让你的诊所蓬勃发展！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075060/extras/4dba6fa52cb5d25bb3832e69dc1cee98.poster.avif?t=1766945750\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075060/extras/4dba6fa52cb5d25bb3832e69dc1cee98.webm?t=1766945750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075060/extras/4dba6fa52cb5d25bb3832e69dc1cee98.mp4?t=1766945750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>解锁更多手术</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入医学领域，你将不断发现更多内容。随着游戏进展，解锁新的诊断工具和治疗方法。从常规检查到罕见疾病，每个病例都将挑战你的医疗专业知识。<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是执行高级医疗手术，还是不断精进自身技能，<i>Doctor Life Simulator</i> 都会推动你成为最优秀的医生。<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075060/extras/1251342a81793f5347a935e745efe112.poster.avif?t=1766945750\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075060/extras/1251342a81793f5347a935e745efe112.webm?t=1766945750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075060/extras/1251342a81793f5347a935e745efe112.mp4?t=1766945750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>叙事世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<i>Doctor Life Simulator</i>中，病人不仅仅是数字，他们是有情感、有故事的人。每一次问诊都是一个探索精彩故事的机会，从温馨时刻到扣人心弦的剧情。<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会遇到相信脉轮失衡的灵修者、在健康与压力间挣扎的职场人士，甚至是一些根本没生病的患者。你的选择和互动将决定病人如何看待你，既作为医生，也作为一个人。<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Doctor Life Simulator</i>不仅是一款游戏，更是一场深入医学世界的旅程。立即将其加入Steam愿望单，准备拯救生命，一个诊断接一个诊断！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>真实的医疗程序</strong>：进行详细而逼真的诊断、手术和急救护理。<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/*]</p></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>复杂的患者病例</strong>：治疗从普通疾病到罕见危重病症的各种患者。<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/*]</p></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>医院管理</strong>：建立并扩展你的医院，管理资源，合理规划预算，让医院不断发展。<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/*]</p></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>时间管理</strong>：时间至关重要，迅速诊断、进行手术，并做出关键决策，以拯救病人并确保医院正常运转。<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/*]</p></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>医疗工具和设备</strong>：使用真实的医疗仪器和先进技术治疗病人。<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/*]</p></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>互动剧情</strong>：参与精彩的剧情，挑战你的医学知识和决策能力。<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/*]</p></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul></p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p>",
